<inglise> Article 7 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> Five years after the date referred to in Article 6 (2), the Council, acting on a proposal from the Commission, shall examine and, upon a Commission proposal and in cooperation with the European Parliament, if need be, revise Article 2 (4), in the light of the experience acquired in applying this Directive and of the aim of eliminating the additional information referred to in Article 2 (4), taking account of the progress made in striving towards the harmonization of the accounts of banks and other financial institutions. </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu uurib komisjoni ettepanekul ning vajaduse korral korrigeerib komisjoni ettepanekul ja koost&ouml;&ouml;s Euroopa Parlamendiga artikli 2 l&otilde;iget 4 viis aastat p&auml;rast artikli 6 l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud kuup&auml;eva, pidades silmas k&auml;esoleva direktiivi kohaldamisel omandatud kogemusi ja eesm&auml;rki k&otilde;rvaldada artikli 2 l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud t&auml;iendava teabe n&otilde;ue, v&otilde;ttes seejuures arvesse pankade ja muude finantseerimisasutuste aastaaruannete koosk&otilde;lastamiseks tehtud edusamme. </eesti>
